    "Its accuracy is at 0.82 and f1-score at 0.79 which is more than both ELECTRA variants and similar to Nor-BERT small, suggesting a wellrounded performance.",
    "Scandi-BERT and nb-BERT base, both with precision at 0.79 and recall at 0.81, demonstrate a similar capability in correctly classifying instances, and both maintain an accuracy of 0.81.",
